ore":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d52a626a7f7e84ad5cba737ace7c3c14b4ae46b","tid":1980504,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLnvMKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLnvMKE.jpg&h=f8821185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n子瑜18日在唱歌練習室開直播，一開始選擇濾鏡時感覺相當苦惱，但其實素顏狀況很好，沒想到直播快20分鐘時，她才被提醒牙縫有菜渣，瞪大雙眼且轉過鏡頭後便大方用舌頭清。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1WuaMKU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WuaMKU.png&h=6df57b59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hFCjE5a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFCjE5a.png&h=7f3d214f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邊清的同時子瑜還說「卡（菜渣）了！都沒人跟我說，卡在牙齒上了，ONCE（官方粉絲名稱）都看到了，ONCE為什麼不說，怎麼辦！ONCE都看到了！不過沒關係啦&hellip;這也是有可能發生的事情」，直率的反應讓粉絲直呼好可愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4827/4827315.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4827%2F4827315.jpg&h=8bd40596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜一開始聽到自己卡菜渣很震驚。（圖／翻攝自TWICE VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n另外，出道以來子瑜常常被稱讚姿勢端正，對此她透露其實自己有很多壞習慣，最近很認真上皮拉提斯，害羞笑說：「其實以前也有上，只是不太常去。」<br />\n<br />\n說到這裡還被經紀人吐槽「一年去一次」，子瑜則說最近一周去2天還握拳跟自己喊話：「希望可以繼續維持這個運動習慣，皮拉提斯真的很好，平常沒用到的肌肉都被訓練到了，所以跳舞的時候也有點不太一樣。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:18:36.000Z","msg":"印賓樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e69692a6eaf38022490d952c7ef9f86361ac2c","tid":1980504,"uid":324234,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:41:57.000Z","msg":"開始有少少大陸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1223277e01885454061ae75033bb45109e063b","tid":1980504,"uid":31999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"PR公司五毛狗"},{"pid":"c6f98b4748e60